c: 19
v: 75
t: "Yithi (Muhammad) Nabani na lowo uphambukileyo, uSozincebamakamolulele(ngokumandiselaubutyebinexesha lokuphila) bade bakubone oko babesoloko bethenjiswa ngako okungaba sisohlwayo okanye ibe yiYure, baza kwazi okokuba ngubani na okwimeko emaxongo, ingubani na ekungekho yakhe ngokwemikhosi"